{"tid":1498471,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"9月1日 全港女士入機場 向國際求救","createTime":"2019-08-23T12:01:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T12:52:52.000Z","uid":94499,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"224df491556143d833fddc423eb0c302f30f3bd3","tid":1498471,"uid":94499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T12:01:23.000Z","msg":"原post : 強烈要求舉行 全港女士大遊行 ！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1497944\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1497944</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我知道隔離post有寫9月8推遊行，<br />\n但真係等唔到再多一日，可以其實隨時行得！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">]因為真係好撚嬲到屌佢老母</span></span><br />\n當然真係好想女權幫幫我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果地點唔適合，歡迎提議，歡迎討論！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/F-kZRbHWkHU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FF-kZRbHWkHU&d=3B0aCwotxrbiSqfA1QWlAu2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=f1845e1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/F-kZRbHWkHU</a><br />\n<br />\n如果無人搞到，我願意第一個企出嚟！"},{"pid":"9416631e56864b9eea7c6b6d28954d1fb6226f68","tid":1498471,"uid":94499,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T12:03:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n集會出現左<br />\n<br />\n集會主題：反送中#Metoo集會<br />\n主辦：平等機會婦女聯席<br />\n日期：8月28日 （三）<br />\n時間：晚上7:30 （暫定）<br />\n申請地點：遮打花園<br />\n*不反對通知書申請中"},{"pid":"b80090e81b40d5ca83fb2a6bbcb2401cb43e1c99","tid":1498471,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T12:10:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">824朝早機場要車</span></span>"},{"pid":"5bfdbccf70